= render 'shared/why_richmond'

.row
  .large-7.columns.margin-bottom-30
    %section
      .header-image
        = image_tag 'keeton_family.jpg', alt: 'The Keetons'
      %p
        As a native to the Richmond Area, I have grown up loving this part of
        the state. With our close proximity to the coast and the beautiful
        Blue Ridge mountains, central Virginia has so much to offer.
      %p
        I have extensive knowledge of the area and I am passionate about
        real estate. However, my ultimate goal is to surpass my clients
        expectations of personal service as a Realtor and work as hard as I can
        to make the best deal possible.
      %p
        If you're looking to buy or sell real estate in our area, I'd love to
        have the opportunity to work with you. Feel free to call
        %strong 804-921-7406,
        send me an
        = "#{link_to('email', 'mailto:danielspencerkeeton@gmail.com', class: 'underline')},".html_safe
        or send me a
        = link_to 'Facebook message.', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Daniel-Keeton-Real-Estate/157662247658325', class: 'underline', target: '_blank'
      %footer
        %p
          %span.strong Daniel Keeton,
          %span.italic Realtor

  .large-5.columns.margin-bottom-30
    - unless @post.nil?
      = render 'posts/post', post: @post, preview: true

    .feature-image
      = link_to image_tag('richmond/uva-rotunda.jpg'), 'http://www.visitcharlottesville.org/',
                target: '_blank'
      .content
        %p
          %strong Charlottesville -
          beautiful city only 45 minutes from Richmond!

    %section
      %header
        %h3 Testimonials
      %ul.testimonials
        = render 'testimonials/testimonial', testimonial: @testimonial

